    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "/**\n * Code: Build Xenith Payin Requests\n * \n * Menyusun request body untuk pembuatan payin ke XenithPay API.\n * \n * Input:\n *   - Form: Create Invoice -> initiated_amount, phone_number, referenceCode, email, customerName, description\n *   - Postgres: Get Payment Channel -> method, channel\n * \n * Output:\n *   - signaturePayload: string payload yang akan di-sign dengan HMAC-SHA256\n *   - timestamp: ISO timestamp untuk header Xenith-Request-Timestamp\n *   - body: object request body untuk POST /v1/payins\n * \n * Catatan:\n *   - customerReference diisi dengan email sebagai contoh (bisa diganti identifier lain)\n *   - callbackUrl HARUS mengarah ke path yang sama dengan node 'Webhook: Xenith Payin Callback'\n *     yaitu /webhook/xenith-payin-sandbox. Jika tidak cocok, callback dari XenithPay\n *     tidak akan diterima dan flow Callback Payin tidak akan berjalan.\n *   - Ganti domain/base URL ke URL publik N8N Anda (ngrok/domain production)\n * \n * Webhook URL di N8N (node Webhook: Xenith Payin Callback):\n *   - Test URL       : http://<n8n-host>/webhook-test/xenith-payin-sandbox\n *   - Production URL : http://<n8n-host>/webhook/xenith-payin-sandbox\n *   callbackUrl HARUS menggunakan format Production URL (/webhook/), bukan Test URL\n *   (/webhook-test/), karena XenithPay mengirim callback saat workflow aktif (production mode).\n *   Test URL hanya aktif saat klik 'Listen for test event' di N8N UI.\n * \n * Environment API:\n *   - Sandbox    : https://openapi.sandbox.xenithpay.com/v1/payins\n *   - Production : https://openapi.xenithpay.com/v1/payins\n *   Ganti URL di node 'HTTP: Create Xenith Payin' saat pindah ke production.\n */\n\n// Susun request body dari data form dan payment channel DB\nconst body = {\n      initiatedAmount: $('Form: Create Invoice').first().json.initiated_amount,\n      currency: 'IDR',\n      paymentMethod: $input.first().json.method,\n      paymentChannel: $input.first().json.channel,\n      customerPhoneNumber: $('Form: Create Invoice').first().json.phone_number.toString(),\n      referenceCode: $('Form: Create Invoice').first().json.referenceCode,\n      customerReference: $('Form: Create Invoice').first().json.email,\n      customerName: $('Form: Create Invoice').first().json.customerName,\n      description: $('Form: Create Invoice').first().json.description,\n      // callbackUrl harus menggunakan Production URL (/webhook/), bukan Test URL (/webhook-test/)\n      // dan harus cocok dengan path di node 'Webhook: Xenith Payin Callback'\n      callbackUrl: 'https://harlee-phylogenetic-nonequivocally.ngrok-free.dev/webhook/xenith-payin-sandbox',\n      redirectUrl: \"https://www.weselaja.com/\",\n    };\n\n// Susun signature payload sesuai format XenithPay: METHOD\\nURI\\nTIMESTAMP\\nBODY\nconst method = \"POST\";\nconst uri = \"/v1/payins\";\nconst timestamp = new Date().toISOString();\nconst signaturePayload = `${method}\\n${uri}\\n${timestamp}\\n${JSON.stringify(body)}`;\n\nreturn {\n  json:{signaturePayload, timestamp, body}\n}"
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [
        720,
