      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "/**\n * Code: Build Xenith Payout Payload\n * \n * Menyusun request body untuk pembuatan payout (disbursement) ke XenithPay API.\n * \n * Input:\n *   - Form: Create Payout -> amount, destinationPayoutAccount, destinationPayoutAccountName, email\n *   - Postgres: Get Payout Channel -> method, channel\n * \n * Output:\n *   - signaturePayload: string payload yang akan di-sign dengan HMAC-SHA256\n *   - timestamp: ISO timestamp untuk header Xenith-Request-Timestamp\n *   - body: object request body untuk POST /v1/payouts\n * \n * Catatan:\n *   - customerReference diisi dengan email sebagai contoh (bisa diganti identifier lain)\n *   - callbackUrl HARUS mengarah ke path yang sama dengan node 'Webhook: Xenith Payout Callback'\n *     yaitu /webhook/xenith-payout-sandbox. Jika tidak cocok, callback dari XenithPay\n *     tidak akan diterima dan flow Callback Payout tidak akan berjalan.\n *   - Ganti domain/base URL ke URL publik N8N Anda (ngrok/domain production)\n * \n * Webhook URL di N8N (node Webhook: Xenith Payout Callback):\n *   - Test URL       : http://<n8n-host>/webhook-test/xenith-payout-sandbox\n *   - Production URL : http://<n8n-host>/webhook/xenith-payout-sandbox\n *   callbackUrl HARUS menggunakan format Production URL (/webhook/), bukan Test URL\n *   (/webhook-test/), karena XenithPay mengirim callback saat workflow aktif (production mode).\n *   Test URL hanya aktif saat klik 'Listen for test event' di N8N UI.\n * \n * Environment API:\n *   - Sandbox    : https://openapi.sandbox.xenithpay.com/v1/payouts\n *   - Production : https://openapi.xenithpay.com/v1/payouts\n *   Ganti URL di node 'HTTP: Create Xenith Payout' saat pindah ke production.\n */\n\nconst method = \"POST\";\nconst uri = \"/v1/payouts\";\nconst timestamp = new Date().toISOString();\n\n// Susun request body dari data form dan payout channel DB\nconst body = {\n  initiatedAmount: $('Form: Create Payout').first().json.amount,\n  currency: \"IDR\",\n  destinationPayoutMethod: $input.first().json.method,\n  destinationPayoutChannel: $input.first().json.channel,\n  destinationPayoutAccount: $('Form: Create Payout').first().json.destinationPayoutAccount,\n  destinationPayoutAccountName: $('Form: Create Payout').first().json.destinationPayoutAccountName,\n  referenceCode: \"REF-TEST-001\",\n  customerReference: $('Form: Create Payout').first().json.email,\n  description: \"Payout merchant TEST MERCHANT 2026-01-01\",\n  // callbackUrl harus menggunakan Production URL (/webhook/), bukan Test URL (/webhook-test/)\n  // dan harus cocok dengan path di node 'Webhook: Xenith Payout Callback'\n  callbackUrl: \"https://harlee-phylogenetic-nonequivocally.ngrok-free.dev/webhook/xenith-payout-sandbox\"\n}\n\n// Susun signature payload sesuai format XenithPay: METHOD\\nURI\\nTIMESTAMP\\nBODY\nconst signaturePayload = `${method}\\n${uri}\\n${timestamp}\\n${JSON.stringify(body)}`;\n\nreturn {json:{signaturePayload,timestamp,body}}\n"
      },
