    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "# Payout\n\n## Prasyarat\n- Buat credential **PostgreSQL** di N8N (Settings > Credentials)\n- Buat tabel `payout_channels` dengan kolom: `id`, `method`, `channel`, `name`, `created_at`\n- Seed data dari file `payout_channels_rows.sql` pada https://github.com/RudyThongWeselAja/N8NWeselAja/blob/main/payout_channels_rows.sql\n## Alur\nForm > Postgres: Get Payout Channel > Code: Build Payload > Crypto: Sign > Crypto: Idempotency > HTTP: Create Payout\n",
